data.description: If you are looking for a home to make your own, this home is a blank slate waiting for you.  Galley kitchen, dining area, and extra large family room are perfect for large gatherings.  Separate living room.  Aggregate flooring throughout the living areas and wood laminate in the bedrooms.  Spacious backyard for play or entertaining.  Top rated schools.  This spacious home offers endless possibilities. Roof, A/C, and exterior paint are approximately 6 years old.
